title: George Gee interviews Big Band Leader Count Basie in 12/9/79
description:
George Gee interviews legendary Big Band LeaderCount Basie in the dressing room at Carnegie Music Hall in Pittsburgh, PA on December 9th, 1979 for WRCT Radio.
